description: Redevelopment of the site including partial demolition and retention of the west facade and erection of a mansard roof at 53-59 Old Town, together with the erection of 7 new buildings with a maximum of 6 storeys to provide 170 residential accommodations including 68 affordable housing units and retail (Class A1), Restaurants and Cafes (Class A3) and offices (Class B1), plus provision of 76 parking spaces and 173 cycles stands at basement, amenity spaces and landscaping and boundary treatments.
